Yes, right now at this spot, naturally we were with Uncle
Ali, we are in the middle of Mezra'a (Farm) village.

213
00:11:27,000 --> 00:11:31,000
Magû em gihiştine nîzîkê 'Ebîdanê. Teb'en cîyê xwe jî...
 
