I see.

256
00:14:22,000 --> 00:14:25,000
Koze, berê çi dikiribû? Koze.
 
Koze, what was it doing before? Koze.

257
00:14:25,000 --> 00:14:27,000
Koze muselxane.
 
Koze was an armory/post.

258
